import React from 'react' import './HeavySnow.css' export default function HeavySnow() { function getRandom(min, max) { return Math.random() * (max - min) + min; } const snowflakes = document.querySelectorAll('.snowflakeHeavy'); for (let i = 0; i < snowflakes.length; i++) { const snowflake = snowflakes[i] console.log(snowflake.style.width); snowflake.setAttribute('cx', getRandom(1,100) + '%'); snowflake.setAttribute('cy', '-10%'); snowflake.setAttribute('fill', 'white'); snowflake.setAttribute('r', `${parseInt(snowflake.style.width) / 2}px`); } return(
) }
